{"tid":259704,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳：港男拍縮時片揚威國際 - 李八方","createTime":"2017-05-27T07:00:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T17:48:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6556052ddc6cc4c560cc7c57c4ba44d3ef142823","tid":259704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:00:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20035367&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20035367%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170527&d=mtfeo3%2FFxBxsCB1Lo%2FrDY10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=049a2ee0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20035367%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170527&h=b680101b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20035367&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170527</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n港男拍縮時片揚威國際 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n專欄專論&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n香港攝影師蘇嘉進（Francis）再度揚威國際！佢用縮時攝影（timelapse）及超行縮影拍攝嘅短片《ESCAPE》，喺今屆葡萄牙電影藝術及旅遊節「Finisterra Arr&aacute;bida Film Art &amp; Tourism Festival」中，獲得最佳音樂視頻第二名。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\nFrancis花半年時間記錄郊外天堂同都市嘅美景。《ESCAPE》短片截圖<br />\n<br />\n呈現港美景及打工苦況<br />\n<br />\n佢話今次係首次用人物主導創作短片，能夠係芸芸高水準作品中脫穎而出，十分驚喜。<br />\n《ESCAPE》講嘅係香港人從工作地獄逃脫到郊外天堂嘅故事。Francis用咗半年時間，將中環、金鐘、尖沙嘴繁忙都市人與事，同埋飛鵝山、大澳、大帽山等美麗風景記錄低，並以人物主導，將香港人係「全球最長工時城市」打工苦況呈現。<br />\nFrancis話，香港工作環境極不平衡，每個人只係掛住工作，係生存唔係生活，其實好悲慘；又話工時過長，令人忽略好多值得去做嘅事，包括陪伴家人、花時間自我調整心靈，希望港人能夠反思。<br />\n想欣賞獲獎短片，可以去以下連結：&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/franso/videos/1333048266732449/￼\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffranso%2Fvideos%2F1333048266732449%2F%EF%BF%BC&d=mtfeo3%2FFxBxsCB1Lo%2FrDY10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=cc5c8ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/franso/videos/1333048266732449/￼</a><br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=mtfeo3%2FFxBxsCB1Lo%2FrDY10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=ed1efecc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"8e49d1f65769c83d6fe48d9883493f97e680eafc","tid":259704,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:01:06.000Z","msg":"Francis花半年時間記錄郊外天堂同都市嘅美景。《ESCAPE》短片截圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170527/large/27lp2p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170527%2Flarge%2F27lp2p04.jpg&h=9e4a1ec6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffd721ac066db56500ffb01b2a0bf89f205b5d3a","tid":259704,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"勁啊"},{"pid":"d6ba36f5418bf30d48939a1bc962b55ee694d399","tid":259704,"uid":92664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"睇完片真心覺得靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c78156ada8a8a68857daaca2dba243dd13420da","tid":259704,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:30:02.000Z","msg":"等睇專家"},{"pid":"858a5ed82ddec3dd1f386bfaca9d9f0f67ba1781","tid":259704,"uid":73613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ee430737467c4041c138570b6d09e6ced922ca8","tid":259704,"uid":10157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"D郊外景拍到好靚<br />\n令到我諗澳洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62435281dfeb45264bcc0a3557aaaa9b79cf6376","tid":25970